<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">About Lost & Found</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted">Reuniting people with their belongings since 2024</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                The Lost & Found Management System was created to help our campus community 
                easily report and find lost items. We understand how stressful it can be to 
                lose something important, and we're here to help.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our platform provides a centralized, easy-to-use system where anyone can 
                report lost or found items, search for their belongings, and connect with 
                finders to reclaim their possessions.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="mb-4 mt-5">How to Use</h3>
            <div class="accordion" id="howToUse">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
                            Reporting a Lost Item
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#howToUse">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Click on "Report Lost Item", fill in the details including what you lost, 
                            where you last saw it, and your contact information. Upload a photo if you have one.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
                            Reporting a Found Item
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#howToUse">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Found something? Click "Report Found Item" and provide details about what you found 
                            and where. This helps the owner identify and claim their belongings.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
                            Claiming an Item
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#howToUse">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            If you find your item in our listings, use the contact information provided 
                            to reach out to the finder. Verify ownership and arrange for pickup.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="bg-light p-4 rounded">
                <h3 class="mb-4">Quick Stats</h3>
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center bg-white">
                            <i class="fas fa-users fa-2x text-primary mb-2"></i>
                            <h4>500+</h4>
                            <small class="text-muted">Active Users</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center bg-white">
                            <i class="fas fa-boxes fa-2x text-success mb-2"></i>
                            <h4>1000+</h4>
                            <small class="text-muted">Items Reported</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center bg-white">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake fa-2x text-warning mb-2"></i>
                            <h4>85%</h4>
                            <small class="text-muted">Success Rate</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center bg-white">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock fa-2x text-info mb-2"></i>
                            <h4>24hrs</h4>
                            <small class="text-muted">Avg. Response Time</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-primary text-white rounded">
                <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-2"></i> Tips for Success</h4>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>Provide detailed descriptions of items</li>
                    <li>Upload clear photos when possible</li>
                    <li>Include specific location details</li>
                    <li>Keep your contact information up to date</li>
                    <li>Check the listings regularly</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
